00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:05,220
[Song Dynastypedia]

808
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:06,660
[Local Enrollment Started in the Song Dynasty!]

809
00:43:06,660 --> 00:43:07,160
[Narrator: Xia Meng]

810
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:09,000
Did you know?

811
00:43:09,520 --> 00:43:12,520
Local enrollment began in the Song Dynasty.

812
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:15,440
Back then, the imperial examination was highly competitive,

813
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:17,960
and preliminary exam spots were allocated by region.

814
00:43:18,440 --> 00:43:20,790
This led to frequent cases of examination migration.

815
00:43:22,070 --> 00:43:22,790
So,

816
00:43:22,790 --> 00:43:25,150
to prevent these abuses,

817
00:43:25,550 --> 00:43:28,280
the Song rulers continuously refined the household registration system.

818
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,870
Examinees had to be registered locally

819
00:43:30,870 --> 00:43:32,240
and take their preliminary exams in their place of origin.

820
00:43:32,760 --> 00:43:35,520
They were forbidden from falsifying identities, impersonating others,

821
00:43:35,760 --> 00:43:37,390
or forging family ties.

822
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:39,100
[Household registration information]

823
00:43:39,120 --> 00:43:40,310
They were even subjected to a three-generation background check,

824
00:43:40,720 --> 00:43:43,200
ensuring their character

825
00:43:44,070 --> 00:43:45,480
and that of their fathers and grandfathers

826
00:43:45,480 --> 00:43:46,790
was free from offenses

827
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:48,630
like rebellion or disrespect.

828
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:50,240
These regulations

829
00:43:50,630 --> 00:43:51,280
[Examination Hall]

830
00:43:51,310 --> 00:43:53,240
effectively upheld the integrity of the exam system.

831
00:43:54,760 --> 00:43:57,720
So, Mo checked his household registration before taking the exam,

832
00:43:58,000 --> 00:44:00,310
and urgently sought to know his true identity

833
00:44:00,310 --> 00:44:01,200
to enroll in the Imperial Academy.

834
00:44:02,550 --> 00:44:03,280
This action

835
00:44:03,280 --> 00:44:04,380
was very much in line

836
00:44:04,380 --> 00:44:06,440
with the imperial examination background of the Song Dynasty.

